bbcode_text = "QuickTileset example - unknown tile size

This example uses a [code]Texture[/code] with an unknown cell size.  The [code]TileSet[/code] can be adjusted to set [code]cell_size[/code], and the [code]TileSet[/code] will be updated automatically.

1. Select the [code]QuickTileset[/code] node

2. Drag and drop the [code]kenney_tiny_dungeon_tilemap_packed.png[/code] file onto the [code]Texture[/code] field of the QuickTileset node.  

3. The [code]TileSet[/code] should be automatically created, but the tiles will be of the default size (64x64 px)

4.  Update the [code]cell_size[/code] to (16, 16).  The tiles within the [code]TileSet[/code] will be automatically updated to the correct size

Tiles used in this example are kindly provided by [url=https://kenney.nl/]Kenney.nl[/url]
[url]https://kenney.nl/assets/tiny-dungeon[/url]"
